local storeBundleEntryFrame: Frame? = (lobbyFrame:FindFirstChild("StoreBundleFrame") or (if bottomButtonsFrame then bottomButtonsFrame:FindFirstChild("StoreBundleFrame") else nil)) :: Frame?
